org.apache.polygene.library.sql.generator.implementation.transformation

Class DefaultSQLProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.polygene.library.sql.generator.implementation.transformation.DefaultSQLProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SQLProcessorAggregator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DerbyProcessor, H2Processor, MySQLProcessor, PostgreSQLProcessor, SQLiteProcessor

    public class DefaultSQLProcessor
extends Object
implements SQLProcessorAggregator
    This is base class for processing the SQL syntax elements defined in API. It contains the default processors for nearly all default syntax elements, and a way to easily extend this class in order to add custom processors, or replace default processors with custom ones.
